---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="CRM Case Study: 200+ Leads Managed | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="How a Seattle-area transportation company went from spreadsheet chaos to 200+ managed leads, AI follow-ups & automated daily operations."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-950 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Text side -->
        <div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-400 bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">CRM & Automation</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mt-4 mb-6">From Spreadsheet Chaos to 200+ Managed Leads</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">How a Seattle-area transportation company automated their entire sales operation — and got their evenings back.</p>
          <a href="/contact/?service=crm" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors text-lg">
            Request a Free Discovery Call →
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Image side -->
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/hero-casestudy1.jpg" alt="Transportation company CRM showing lead pipeline with 200+ managed leads and automated follow-ups" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/10 w-full" />
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-teal-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Challenge -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">The Challenge</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">The Challenge</h2>
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>A growing Seattle-area transportation company was drowning in manual work. Customer inquiries came in through email, phone, and their website — but there was no system to track them. The owner was spending hours each day hunting through inboxes, manually tracking quotes, and losing potential customers to slow follow-up.</p>
        <p>He'd tried off-the-shelf CRM platforms, but nothing matched his actual workflow: a high-touch, phone-first sales process with variable pricing, seasonal demand, and long booking lead times.</p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-navy-950">The core problem: Leads were falling through the cracks. By the time a follow-up went out, the customer had already booked with a competitor.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">What We Built</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">What We Built</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">🖥️ Custom CRM Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">A purpose-built CRM with pipeline stages matching the company's actual sales process. Every lead gets tracked from first inquiry through completed job. The system manages 200+ leads across multiple pipeline stages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">🤖 AI Email Agents (2 Personas)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Two AI-powered email personas, each with a distinct voice — one warm and enthusiastic for initial outreach, one calm and professional for logistics and confirmations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">📧 Automated Daily Briefing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Every morning, the owner receives one email with everything he needs: which leads need attention today, upcoming events, outstanding payments, and pipeline health.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">🔄 Real-Time System Sync</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Bi-directional sync between the CRM, email, and the company's existing booking platform. Everything stays in sync without manual entry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 md:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">💳 Payment Tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Integrated payment processing with deposit tracking, payment link generation, and automatic reconciliation. The owner sees exactly who has paid, who hasn't, and how much is outstanding — at a glance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Results</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">The Results</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">48h → 5min</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Lead response time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">200+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Leads tracked & managed</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">15+ hrs/wk</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Manual work eliminated</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">2</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">AI email personas</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">1 email</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Daily business overview</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">99%+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">System uptime</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Stack -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-center">Technology Used</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
        {['Custom CRM', 'AI Email Agents', 'Real-Time Monitoring', 'Payment Integration', 'Automated Scheduling', 'Cloud Infrastructure'].map(tech => (
          <span class="text-xs bg-white text-slate-600 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200">{tech}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust + Links -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic mb-8">References available on request.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm">
        <a href="/services/crm/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium transition-colors">See our CRM services →</a>
        <a href="/services/ai/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium transition-colors">See our AI automation services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Want Results Like These?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">Every project starts with a free discovery call. Tell us what's broken — we'll tell you how to fix it.</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service=crm" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Discovery Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Our Work", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Transportation CRM Case Study", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/transportation-crm/" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "Article",
          "headline": "From Spreadsheet Chaos to 200+ Managed Leads",
          "description": "How a Seattle-area transportation company went from spreadsheet chaos to 200+ managed leads, AI follow-ups & automated daily operations.",
          "url": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/transportation-crm/",
          "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "OpsHQ Digital", "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "OpsHQ Digital", "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "mainEntityOfPage": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/transportation-crm/"
        }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
